{"tid":1633047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門人 請留意！同高志森有關！","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:16:25.000Z","uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0703197baec504751cf675383036c8c8b8717847","tid":1633047,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:07:03.000Z","msg":"春天舞台<br />\n係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">高志森</span></span></strong>嘅劇台劇公司 專做垃圾 呃啲觀眾錢 糧又出得低（全行都知）<br />\n低智森係咩人都唔洗再解釋啦<br />\n而佢間公司衣家係屯門大會堂嘅場地伙伴<br />\n<br />\n大家喺出面見到佢啲傳單 banner 就識做啦？<br />\n<br />\n春天舞台<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.springtime.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.springtime.com.hk%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4kzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=1d724002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.springtime.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDWgtfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDWgtfw.png&h=1954456e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門大會堂 場地伙伴 連結如下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/tc/tmth/vp/SAG.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ftmth%2Fvp%2FSAG.html&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4kzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=d3846172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/tc/tmth/vp/SAG.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係同時屯門大會堂又有個叫普劇場嘅場地伙伴<br />\n據我所知係黃嘅 小心唔好殺錯隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n（真黃 非曲線 特大字希望唔好搞錯對像）"},{"pid":"83be9a4968716b07bb2c23024d06216b2905fdc9","tid":1633047,"uid":247860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"幫佢貼美國旗，話晒佢真係有美國國藉喎，但又咁愛國？<br />\n<br />\n貼滿後比所羅門啦"},{"pid":"3b66b3e195a459bfe574742ec552b6089b5a0d46","tid":1633047,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"想推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1f48392fd2fda006c4c20e4da02c4f2aa40360","tid":1633047,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">幫我click入去推</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非戰場－面具人鏈</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">外國嘅人好幸福，一出世就生活係民主國家，有部分人根本唔會明點解我地爭取民主要用裝修、神獸（唔好高估外國人嘅智力，佢地睇野好表面）。</span><br />\n<br />\n有位巴講得好啱，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之所以漸漸少咗國際支持，係因為和理非戰場越來越細</span></span>。冇和理非嘅活動吸引佢地嘅眼球，餘下嘅只有神獸同裝修。<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，我地可以搞返個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">面具人鏈</span></span>，表達我地不畏反蒙面法，不畏極權嘅精神。<br />\n人鏈活動一直都比較少人被人拉，比起遊行更適合一家大細出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我地日日遊行，係外國人眼中好悶㗎。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要有多啲gimmick佢地先會重新關注</span></span>。<br />\n時間、地點我唔知應該點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如果真係搞面具人鏈，我地可以帶上自製嘅四川面譜、facepainting、動物面膜、超人、Mario、多啦A夢、V煞⋯⋯冇嘅話純戴口罩都得，不過口罩上可以畫野。總之約精彩越好玩越好<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家好需要一個嘉年華式抗爭</span></span>去緩和下大家嘅情緒，同獲得國際認同。好似之前雷射革命咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果各位手足覺得呢個建議ok，就開多另一個po去講時間地點啦。<br />\n（大家都要考慮一個問題就係，面具人鏈會唔會被狗拉，如果會嘅話⋯⋯都係諗諗先。畢竟expect一家大細出席，怕會全家被告）<br />\n<br />\np牌求推"},{"pid":"94a698b9fbc918845776d9a7db7ad2f8148dc0c3","tid":1633047,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}